WEBVTT

00:01.610 --> 00:03.032
Blue:
PreVIously on
"Queen Sugar"...

00:03.090 --> 00:06.730
Dad, this is my fianc,
Ralph Angel Bordelon.

00:06.780 --> 00:09.260
- Nice to meet you,
Mr. and Mrs. Sutton.
- Nice to meet you.

00:09.310 --> 00:12.438
Doctor: Considering
your symptoms, I think
we can safely diagnose you.

00:12.490 --> 00:13.741
Lupus.

00:13.790 --> 00:16.782
Nova:
I can't be all of me

00:16.840 --> 00:18.535
when I'm with you.

00:18.580 --> 00:20.889
You don't see
a future for us?

00:20.930 --> 00:23.057
- I just want
to be with you.
- Wait.

00:24.500 --> 00:26.149
Please don't hate me.

00:26.200 --> 00:28.065
Darla:
Blue...

00:28.110 --> 00:30.453
he might not be yours,
Ralph Angel.

00:30.500 --> 00:31.717
I'm sorry.

00:46.650 --> 00:47.992
Iwish...

00:50.920 --> 00:53.605
I wish I didn't have
to say this to you.

00:56.270 --> 00:57.783
I never wanted
to hurt anyone.

00:57.840 --> 00:59.091
Ijust...

01:02.140 --> 01:04.483
I just wanted us all
to be okay.

01:06.280 --> 01:08.236
That's all
I ever wanted.

01:10.070 --> 01:12.061
Just to be with you.

01:15.290 --> 01:17.679
[crying ]

01:17.720 --> 01:19.199
And Blue.

01:21.120 --> 01:23.429
I don't understand.

01:25.780 --> 01:27.168
What you saying to me?

01:31.000 --> 01:32.900
Don't do this to me.

01:34.350 --> 01:36.432
I'm so sorry.

01:37.920 --> 01:39.820
[crying ]

01:48.320 --> 01:50.231
My eyes

01:53.410 --> 01:55.583
My guide

01:58.980 --> 02:01.722
Waves

02:01.770 --> 02:03.988
Waves

02:04.030 --> 02:06.021
- Waves...
- [ sobbing ]

02:06.080 --> 02:07.160
[ engine starts ]

02:09.470 --> 02:12.166
Waves

02:12.210 --> 02:14.678
Waves

02:14.740 --> 02:18.471
- [ Darla sobbing ]
- Waves.

02:18.520 --> 02:21.307
[ theme music playing ]

02:21.350 --> 02:25.480
Dreams never die,
take flight, as the
world turns

02:25.530 --> 02:28.795
Dreams never die,
take flight, as the world
turns

