Vi, baby,
you are my business.

19:53.400 --> 19:56.358
Now, look,
I know that regular
over-the-counter medication

19:56.410 --> 19:58.628
comes in
a brown paper bag.

19:58.670 --> 20:02.197
Prescriptions
come in a white bag.

20:03.850 --> 20:05.624
There's something
that you ain't telling me.

20:13.820 --> 20:16.380
Sit down, Hollywood.

20:16.430 --> 20:18.819
I don't like the way
you said that.

20:28.000 --> 20:30.560
Doctor says
I have lupus.

20:47.940 --> 20:50.158
There ain't no cure
for that.

20:55.950 --> 20:59.113
Are you trying to tell me
that you are gonna...?

21:00.910 --> 21:03.731
No, no, no.
I'm gonna be fine.

21:05.650 --> 21:08.995
I'm gonna manage it
and live with it.

21:09.050 --> 21:11.564
But I'm gonna live
and I'm gonna live good.

21:15.920 --> 21:18.138
We're gonna
manage it together.

21:23.540 --> 21:25.235
Oh...

21:27.500 --> 21:30.321
If I meant we,
I would've said we.

21:33.680 --> 21:37.320
I'm not gonna be
another Leeanne.

21:37.380 --> 21:40.941
I never want to be
a burden to nobody.

21:40.990 --> 21:43.424
That situation ain't
the same as this one, baby.

21:43.470 --> 21:46.462
I'm not gonna do it, Hollywood.
I'm not gonna do that to you.

21:46.520 --> 21:48.772
Stop talking out the side
of your neck, chre.

21:52.180 --> 21:57.914
Now, I done left my job
to be with you.

21:57.960 --> 22:00.224
Does that sound like somebody
who doesn't wanna be with you

22:00.270 --> 22:02.318
for the rest of their life?

22:06.760 --> 22:08.625
That's not _
a rhetorical question.

22:13.150 --> 22:15.015
No.

22:15.070 --> 22:17.197
No.

22:17.240 --> 22:18.719
No.

22:20.070 --> 22:21.719
No.

22:24.860 --> 22:27.727
Well, rest in that.

22:27.780 --> 22:31.034
Believe in that,
in us.

22:32.960 --> 22:36.919
You said you don't want
to be Leeanne, fine.

22:36.960 --> 22:40.305
Well, I ain't Jimmy Dale.

22:40.350 --> 22:41.954
I'm Hollywood.

22:42.010 --> 22:44.831
And you Vi.

22:44.880 --> 22:47.269
We us.

22:50.930 --> 22:53.319
And they don't matter
in here.

22:55.240 --> 22:57.322
I ain't going nowhere.

23:00.110 --> 23:01.668
Trust...

23:04.030 --> 23:06.248
and we gonna be
all right.

23:08.990 --> 23:10.981
We're gonna get
through this.

23:11.040 --> 23:13.998
All of us.

23:14.040 --> 23:16.474
All of us? No.

23:16.520 --> 23:19.694
No, Hollywood,
I can't put this on them.

23:19.740 --> 23:22.914
- They can't--
- You're letting me
help you.

23:22.960 --> 23:25.918
And I'm gonna
help you tell them.

23:25.960 --> 23:28.918
But we gotta tell them.

23:28.970 --> 23:30.961
You ain't got
no choice in this.

23:33.020 --> 23:36.626
'Cause we done already seen
what secrets can do
to this family.

23:36.670 --> 23:40.458
This is how it begins.

23:48.250 --> 23:50.024
